title: Patch 5.16 Issues?
body: Hey there guys, just wondering if anyone else is having trouble downloading patch 5.16? Been stuck on 33% for some time now scanning files... it's over 9000!!!! Any solutions to this would be greatly appreciated, super keen for a game before class!

replies.body:
Are u people still around cause i know how to fix the thing O:) 

~ORION~

Unfortunately i figured this out too late.

But restart your computer.

Hidden league of legends.exe process is stopping some of the files from being updated because its using them.

And because its hidden you cant close it.
same here..... it says go check log..... i hv no idea
